snippet.title: Phantasy Star Online 2 - Sign up for the Closed Beta Test Now!
snippet.description:
This is the moment you have been waiting for. Phantasy Star Online 2 (PSO2), one of Japan’s biggest online RPGs, is coming to North America on Xbox One in Spring 2020. 

★ Secure your spot for the Closed Beta Test now!
For more information, visit: http://www.pso2.com

★ PSO2 Social
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PSO2Official
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/play_pso2
Twitter: https://twitter.com/play_pso2
